divs: Sighting DetailsI started taking pictures in my car on my camera phone of the sun on my lunch break. Just because I've recently heard of an object near the sun. I took 4 pictures with something that seems to be orbiting the sun. It appears to be a half moon shape. Maybe a satellite?

Summary: Picture of something orbiting the sun
